%  POLICY: cite the PEER-REVIEWED VERSION OF RECORD wherever one exists.
%  Every entry below was checked against a primary source (ACL Anthology, PMLR,
%  MLSys, NeurIPS/ICLR proceedings, ACM DL, IEEE/Crossref, USENIX, DBLP) on
%  2026-07-09 and again on 2026-07-16.
